\begin_layout Standard
In this section we present the methodology to assess the models’ performance.
 Models are ranked based on their RMSE and their MAPE for each period in all three horizons.
 We then use the Diebold-Mariano test to compare each model against the benchmark RW and see how each model competes it.
 We are considering the two econometric models (RW,
 VAR) and six machine learning models (LASSO,
 Ridge,
 LARS,
